[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1483523","time":"2019-8-25 21:03","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"(｡´-д-)","message":"<a href=\"https://bgm.tv/group/topic/352096\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">【中元节特刊】大家讲讲经历过的诡异事件吧</a>","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1483548","time":"2019-8-25 21:51","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"这个帖子发的时候我还没有进入这种到处找故事看的状态，所以完全没注意到……"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/58/285822.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1483525","time":"2019-8-25 21:11","userId":"rog_defwang","userName":"小耳兔","userSign":"(孤独最强)","message":"说个上个月发生的真事儿，当时我在麻醉室轮科，那天值夜班，做完手术送病人回内科楼病房，再回手术室的路上发现楼的侧面有扇小门，我没走过，在想能不能抄近路我就进去了，里面是一条通道，我进去后向前走了大概五六米，然后左拐（前面右边都是墙）又走了十几米米，然后前方是一扇门关着的，牌子上写着是污物室，右边还是墙，左转有个出口，我就出去了，出去之后我发现我还是在进来之前的原地，我很惊讶就再走进去，里面就变成了一条直路，正前方是污物室，左右都是关着的门。然后我再退出去之后沿建筑物一侧走了一遍，也没有发现第二个能进去的小门。<br>当时觉得有点发毛的，不过当医生的毕竟胆子大，也没细想，到现在也没搞清楚咋回事儿。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1483545","time":"2019-8-25 21:48","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"哇这个有意思，不过感觉应该是建筑构造上的问题产生的错觉？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/58/285822.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1483550","time":"2019-8-25 21:53","userId":"rog_defwang","userName":"小耳兔","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 哇这个有意思，不过感觉应该是建筑构造上的问题产生的错觉？</q></div>不知道，完全没理解，我之后也没再尝试进去过那个门"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1483555","time":"2019-8-25 22:01","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">小耳兔</span> 说: 不知道，完全没理解，我之后也没再尝试进去过那个门</q></div>能把你走过的路线画个简图看看吗，我还挺好奇的"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/74/307470.jpg","floor":"#3-4","id":"1483558","time":"2019-8-25 22:04","userId":"307470","userName":"Misuzu","userSign":"","message":"好故事，一本满足"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/58/285822.jpg","floor":"#3-5","id":"1483563","time":"2019-8-25 22:24","userId":"rog_defwang","userName":"小耳兔","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 能把你走过的路线画个简图看看吗，我还挺好奇的</q></div>第一次我所认为的构造<br><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/3e/af/285822_APPrU.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/58/285822.jpg","floor":"#3-6","id":"1483564","time":"2019-8-25 22:24","userId":"rog_defwang","userName":"小耳兔","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 能把你走过的路线画个简图看看吗，我还挺好奇的</q></div>我第二次进去见到的构造<br><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/3e/af/285822_MG99u.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#3-7","id":"1483570","time":"2019-8-25 22:43","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">小耳兔</span> 说: 我第二次进去见到的构造</q></div>太神秘了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/32/11/321161.jpg","floor":"#3-8","id":"1483576","time":"2019-8-25 23:22","userId":"ak1ra","userName":"ak1ra","userSign":"","message":"不小心调了个头吧"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/58/285822.jpg","floor":"#3-9","id":"1483577","time":"2019-8-25 23:35","userId":"rog_defwang","userName":"小耳兔","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">ak1ra</span> 说: 不小心调了个头吧</q></div>或许有可能呢，只能找办法解释了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/19/06/190611.jpg","floor":"#3-10","id":"1483601","time":"2019-8-26 02:07","userId":"nirrocat","userName":"盛夏纷乱","userSign":"","message":"我在想有没可能是左转十来米以后再出来回到的不是起点，而是和起点一模一样的另一个门……但是这就无法解释为什么层主再次走进去以后污物间的门会在正前方……"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/19/06/190611.jpg","floor":"#3-11","id":"1483602","time":"2019-8-26 02:08","userId":"nirrocat","userName":"盛夏纷乱","userSign":"","message":"哦后面说还沿着那一侧走了一遍……这也太可怕了，~<br><br>想了好久，除了真的跑进异空间也没有别的解释了，~<br><br>——<br><br>又想了几下，有没有可能是一个三角形的构造或者弧形的构造？如果是一个三角形，那么就可以解释最终回到了起点，但是不能解释为什么再次回去构造发生了变化……"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#3-12","id":"1483648","time":"2019-8-26 10:24","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">盛夏纷乱</span> 说: 哦后面说还沿着那一侧走了一遍……这也太可怕了，~<br><br>想了好久，除了真的跑进异空间也没有别的解释了，~<br><br>——<br><br>又想了几下，有没有可能是一个三角形的构造或者弧形的构造？如果是一个三角形，那么就可以解释...</q></div>我也想过三角形，然而三角形的话进门必然会有两条路……"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/19/06/190611.jpg","floor":"#3-13","id":"1483781","time":"2019-8-26 19:48","userId":"nirrocat","userName":"盛夏纷乱","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 我也想过三角形，然而三角形的话进门必然会有两条路……</q></div>是的……所以还是好神秘啊"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/96/209662.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1483534","time":"2019-8-25 21:20","userId":"209662","userName":"雨宮蓮","userSign":"(「君は綺麗だ」。)","message":"好奇但又怕的不行<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1483546","time":"2019-8-25 21:48","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"不就是享受这种又害怕又好奇的感觉吗<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/16.gif\" smileid=\"55\" alt=\"(bgm39)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/85/318540.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1483535","time":"2019-8-25 21:24","userId":"318540","userName":"mirrorside","userSign":"","message":"快快快 我最喜欢的鬼故事走起来","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1483549","time":"2019-8-25 21:52","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"gkd"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/26/342667.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1483536","time":"2019-8-25 21:27","userId":"342667","userName":"鋭ちゃん","userSign":"(随意。随己意。意怖，意不欲，意不安稳，不随。又不纵意。 . ...)","message":"很害怕，与灵异沾一点点边的动画和电影绝对不会看。看了那晚会发毛，走路会觉得后面不安全，不看这些的话就什么都不怕……<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br><br>我肯定是信的，正是因为信才会害怕去看，因为看了会招过来……<br><br>自己在现实中倒是无意中听到不少……但是并不觉得害怕，感觉身正影不斜，连噩梦一年都没几个，这些与自己无关吧。我就说个关键词好了：1974年香港“黑野狼事件”","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1483547","time":"2019-8-25 21:51","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"电影之类的我也不看，主要是不太喜欢jump scare，但是文字基本不会有这种情况所以还是挺有兴趣的。<br>话说明明看不行，为什么现实中听就没关系呢<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/26/342667.jpg","floor":"#6-2","id":"1483552","time":"2019-8-25 21:53","userId":"342667","userName":"鋭ちゃん","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 电影之类的我也不看，主要是不太喜欢jump scare，但是文字基本不会有这种情况所以还是挺有兴趣的。<br>话说明明看不行，为什么现实中听就没关系呢</q></div>因为听与自己无关，即使发生了也没关系。看的话自己会带入里面，彷佛就是针对自己一样……<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#6-3","id":"1483554","time":"2019-8-25 21:59","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">鋭ちゃん</span> 说: 因为听与自己无关，即使发生了也没关系。看的话自己会带入里面，彷佛就是针对自己一样……</q></div>其实我刚才洗澡的时候就思考（胡思乱想）了这个问题，人会把自己代入故事里面是不是出于一种学习的本能，也就是说会不自觉地去模拟自身身处故事中的情景以期寻找出某种应对方案，然而对于鬼故事这种毫无逻辑的东西来说无法寻找到合理的应对方式，于是带入后只能体会到单纯的恐惧"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/26/342667.jpg","floor":"#6-4","id":"1483556","time":"2019-8-25 22:01","userId":"342667","userName":"鋭ちゃん","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 其实我刚才洗澡的时候就思考（胡思乱想）了这个问题，人会把自己代入故事里面是不是出于一种学习的本能，也就是说会不自觉地去模拟自身身处故事中的情景以期寻找出某种应对方案，然而对于鬼故事这种毫无逻辑的东西来...</q></div>我觉得还是故事的不可控性吧，如果我遇到了